  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel back to the golden age of gaming with Jimmy Jumps! Jimmy Jumps is a throwback platformer that combines the simplicity of classic platformers with the mechanical depth of speedrunning. Compete for high scores in over 90 hand-crafted levels!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be the Best</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against the clock, find hidden mechanics, collect all the coins, and get your initials on the top of the leaderboard! And, watch out for falling obstacles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/1b69ef59feb148a651e10cb88dfabaed.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/1b69ef59feb148a651e10cb88dfabaed.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/1b69ef59feb148a651e10cb88dfabaed.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve your Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new movement mechanics and traverse levels any way you want. Perfect your skills and collect every coin in record time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/4b26d41d6464bccbb9c4ed4e7c52b05f.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/4b26d41d6464bccbb9c4ed4e7c52b05f.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/4b26d41d6464bccbb9c4ed4e7c52b05f.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome Unique Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weather it be traversing in the dark, dodging obstacles, or unlocking hidden areas, each level is designed with it's own puzzles to be solved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/7ce5389be7c9896789d61ad88f56cc49.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/7ce5389be7c9896789d61ad88f56cc49.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/7ce5389be7c9896789d61ad88f56cc49.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Yourself</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 difficulties to overcome and each difficulty comes with it's own challenges. Beat each difficulty to master the level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/2895d3cba38a6e8ca4f1a3bd7c8f1fc1.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/2895d3cba38a6e8ca4f1a3bd7c8f1fc1.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/2895d3cba38a6e8ca4f1a3bd7c8f1fc1.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel back to the golden age of gaming with Jimmy Jumps! Jimmy Jumps is a throwback platformer that combines the simplicity of classic platformers with the mechanical depth of speedrunning. Compete for high scores in over 90 hand-crafted levels!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be the Best</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against the clock, find hidden mechanics, collect all the coins, and get your initials on the top of the leaderboard! And, watch out for falling obstacles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/1b69ef59feb148a651e10cb88dfabaed.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/1b69ef59feb148a651e10cb88dfabaed.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/1b69ef59feb148a651e10cb88dfabaed.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve your Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new movement mechanics and traverse levels any way you want. Perfect your skills and collect every coin in record time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/4b26d41d6464bccbb9c4ed4e7c52b05f.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/4b26d41d6464bccbb9c4ed4e7c52b05f.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/4b26d41d6464bccbb9c4ed4e7c52b05f.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcome Unique Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weather it be traversing in the dark, dodging obstacles, or unlocking hidden areas, each level is designed with it's own puzzles to be solved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/7ce5389be7c9896789d61ad88f56cc49.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/7ce5389be7c9896789d61ad88f56cc49.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/7ce5389be7c9896789d61ad88f56cc49.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Yourself</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 difficulties to overcome and each difficulty comes with it's own challenges. Beat each difficulty to master the level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/2895d3cba38a6e8ca4f1a3bd7c8f1fc1.poster.avif?t=1773772788\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/2895d3cba38a6e8ca4f1a3bd7c8f1fc1.webm?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4117940/extras/2895d3cba38a6e8ca4f1a3bd7c8f1fc1.mp4?t=1773772788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
