      "review_text": "I enjoyed playing Jimmy Jumps daily during pre-release and I was so pleased to see it on Steam now! Keep up the good work... this is a true vintage-retro gem. My favorite part is the speed-run aspect to it!",
      "timestamp_created": 1773938336
    },
    {
