      "author_steamid": "76561198045072558",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 47,
      "review_text": "Pleasantly surprised by this game, Simple on the surface but the ceiling is endless. I found myself grinding the same level over and over optimizing my movement, trying to save frames where I can. I can feel the passion put into this game. I've been following this game through its development and I am happy to see its full release.",
